NOAA-Aurora

NOAA::Aurora - Simple client for NOAA's Aurora Forecast Service

INSTALLATION

Normally you would expect to use a package manager like cpanm to install as:

    cpanm NOAA::Aurora

But to install this module manually, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

CPAN:
    https://metacpan.org/pod/NOAA::Aurora

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc NOAA::Aurora

Source code and issues on GitHub:
    https://github.com/dkechag/NOAA-Aurora

